Oerlikon Reports SF83 Million First-Half Net Income After Loss

-- B y   P a u l   V e r s c h u u r
-- 
2011-08-17T04:45:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-17/oerlikon-reports-sf83-million-first-half-net-income-after-loss.html
OC Oerlikon Corp. AG reported net
income of 83 million Swiss francs ($104.5 million) in the first
half, compared with a net loss of 50 million francs a year
earlier.  The company also confirmed its full-year earnings guidance
and said it sees “some upside potential in profitability,”
speaking today in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Paul Verschuur in Zurich at 
 pverschuur@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
